parameters:
Director Staro: Long time no see! I'm thrilled to meet the
legendary Dragon Slayer!

Director Staro: Clea-san, it's surprising to see you here!
It seems that everyone from the Adventurer's Guild is
serious about this!
Clea: What kind of story is this all about?
Hey hey, am I the only one dissatisfied?
Clea: Why is Mr. Shimos here!?

Shimos from the Unknown Night: This is my line. Rumor has
it that he's taking on jobs related to the Phantom Thief
Perno...

Shimos from the Unknown Night: You think I'm gonna hand
over this job? I'll be the one to settle the score with the
Phantom Thief Perno.

Director Staro: The grudge is an incident that occurred
during the time of the previous director. The Phantom Thief
Perno infiltrated a crystal warehouse called the Fortress.

Director Staro: What was stolen was just a single coin...!
It's a provocative act to showcase their own abilities!

Director Staro: Although it was written as a 'return', they
are expected to come to steal! That's why I asked Mr. Shimos
to come for security!

Director Staro: This is the notice we received this time. I
will finally avenge the regret of the previous director!

Clea: I have come to return the coin that was borrowed to
all the dear vault keepers.

Clea: This time, at the tavern, while being enveloped in
the scent of violets, we will prepare wine and cheese...

Shimos from the Unknown Night: Now, get out of here, you
nuisance! I'll be the one in charge!
Clea (This notice might be a message from Perno-san to us.)
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Director Staro: I will avenge the regret of the previous
director!

Clea: We managed to make it to the top floor... Perno-san,
right?

Phantom Thief Perno: Haa... haa... I-It's okay. If I place
this coin on the desk, then...

Phantom Thief Perno: A-After we escape, it will be over. I
have obtained permission to use magic... Leave it to me--

Phantom Thief Perno: Finally cornered you! Today, I'll make
you retire as a phantom thief, okay?

Phantom Thief Perno: Hehehe, but still... multiple
presence, so Phantom Thief Perno was a group!

Phantom Thief Perno: Ugh... If only I had a little more
time... I could cast the spell... Ugh...

Clea (Should I go out... but my true identity will
definitely be exposed)

Phantom Thief Perno: Looks like you've given up. If it
turns into a battle, I won't be able to hold back, so be
prepared--

Phantom Thief Perno: Ugh...!? You guys... did you mix in
with the guards...?!

Member of the Pegal Bandit Gang: Thanks to the commotion
caused by Perno, I got the perfect chance to sneak in and
kill you!

Phantom Thief Perno: Thanks to me... as a return favor...
I'll make use of this opportunity!
Phantom Thief Perno: Can you take me home after this?

Member of the Pegal Bandit Gang: W-What are you doing,
you--

Phantom Thief Perno: The main target escaped... sigh, all
that's left are these pathetic small fries...

Phantom Thief Perno: I'm in a really bad mood right now.
Since I didn't get to finish the job, I'll destroy your
entire bandit gang.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Director Staro: A coin on the desk... I'm surprised you
actually returned it.

Director Staro: All the thieves who were infiltrating have
been defeated. The battle with Shimosu of the Unseen Night
was truly impressive!

Male Clerk: This floor also serves as a storage room, so
please be careful not to touch any important documents.

Male Clerk: This month's sales... are really amazing...
sigh, if I could just get a little, I could retire...

Secretary to Director Staro: 'Director Staro has been
greatly taken care of.'
